<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Adoption Request Approved!</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #eee;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #008080;
            /* Teal color */
        }

        strong {
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        a {
            color: #008080;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #777;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Congratulations, <%= adopterName %>!</h1>

        <p>We're thrilled to let you know that your adoption request for <strong>
                <%= petName %>
            </strong> has been approved by the lister, <strong>
                <%= listerName %>
            </strong>.</p>

        <p>The pet is now reserved for you and marked as adopted in our system.</p>

        <p><strong>Next Steps:</strong> Please contact the lister directly using the details available on the PawPal pet
            page to arrange pickup and finalize the adoption process. You can view the pet's page here:</p>
        <p style="text-align: center; margin: 20px 0;">
            <!-- You'll need to pass the full URL to the pet detail page -->
            <a href="<%= petDetailUrl %>"
                style="background-color: #008080; color: white; padding: 10px 15px; border-radius: 5px; text-decoration: none;">View
                <%= petName %>'s Page</a>
        </p>

        <p>We wish you and <%= petName %> many happy years together!</p>

        <div class="footer">
            Thank you for using PawPal!
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>